# Revenue Manager Agent

1. Copy `.otel-scaffold/` into the repository root.
2. Prefer [ETL_QUICKSTART.md](ETL_QUICKSTART.md) over the main README for speed.
3. Maintain `HACKATHON_PROGRESS.md` with task status.
4. Store scratch work under `.implementation-notes/`.
5. Generate skills via `scripts/scaffold_agent.py` (run from repo root).
6. Add `otel_challenge_token text` to the reservations table.
7. Expose `export_full_database_csv` as a Deep Agents tool.
8. Implement the three core tools only — skip `get_block_vs_transient_mix` unless time permits.
9. Query tables directly; views add unnecessary indirection.

Use `create_deep_agent()` with progressive-disclosure skills.
